# Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) Project

## Objective
Analyze restaurant dataset to uncover patterns, trends, and relationships between variables.

## Libraries Used
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Features
- Data preprocessing
- Statistical summaries
- Correlation analysis
- Data visualization
- Trend identification
- Insight generation

## Visualizations
- Correlation Heatmap
- Votes vs Ratings Scatter Plot
- Top 10 Cuisines Bar Chart
- Average Rating by Price Range

## Insights
- Restaurants with higher votes generally tend to have better ratings.
- Certain cuisines are more common in the dataset.
- Price range influences restaurant ratings.
- Correlation analysis helps identify relationships between variables.

## Outcome
Developed analytical thinking and data exploration skills using real-world restaurant data.